WINDOW w AS (
    ORDER BY id
    ROWS BETWEEN CURRENT ROW AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING
    PATTERN (A{0,0} B)
    DEFINE A AS val > 1000, B AS val > 0
)
ORDER BY id;
ERROR:  quantifier bounds must be between 0 and 2147483646 with max >= 1
LINE 6:     PATTERN (A{0,0} B)
                       ^
